These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, house, country
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, indian, spanish, indonesian
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, scooter, jet-ski, airplane
1. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
2. the person driving the airplane is between the indian and the fan of electronic##2
3. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the fan of house##1
5. the italian is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the spanish is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | house      | salsa      | country    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | italian | indian | spanish |
| Transport     | scooter    | airplane       | jet-ski     | snowmobile     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, spinach, orange, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, traveling, video-games, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, martial-arts, family, crime
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
7. the person eating orange is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | kiwi     | pear     | spinach       | orange    |
| Hobby         | traveling | video-games   | skydiving | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | crime    | family | martial-arts    | mystery        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, colombian, turkish, canadian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, parkour, skateboarding
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the turkish##3
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
7. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola | iced-tea  | hot-chocolate    | sprite |
| Nationality   | turkish   | canadian  | spanish  | colombian    |
| Sport         | water-polo    | skateboarding | handball | parkour  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, banana, radish, carrot
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, sports, fantasy, animation
4 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, pony, bird
1. the owner of the mouse is between the person watching sports movies and the person eating grapefruit##2
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
3. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating radish##1
4. the person eating radish is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the horse is the person eating carrot##1
6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person eating banana##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Food          | radish   | grapefruit     | banana | carrot |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | animation | scientific   | sports     |
| Pet           | bird | pony      | mouse     | horse       |

