.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, apricot, peas, broccoli
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, videographer, mechanic, security-guard
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, martial-arts, spy
1. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person eating apricot##3
3. the mechanic is the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the accountant is between the person eating peas and the person eating apricot##2
5. the mechanic is on the right of the security-guard##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
7. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
8. the person eating peas is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
9. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | peas      | broccoli | apricot      | radish |
| Job           | videographer | accountant | security-guard | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | spy   | horror     | adventure   |

