.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, fisherman, software-developer, librarian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, r&b, blues, ambient
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, climbing, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the writer##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is the fan of ambient##1
3. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
5. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
6. the software-developer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
7. the fisherman is on the right of the fan of disco##1
8. the fisherman is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | writer    | fisherman   | software-developer | librarian |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | blues   | ambient         | r&b        |
| Sport         | weightlifting | tennis | climbing         | skateboarding       |

