.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, filmmaking, photography, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, photographer, analyst, project-manager
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, egyptian, nigerian
 1. the turkish is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
 2. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 4. the analyst is on the right of the egyptian##1
 5. the egyptian is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the analyst is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the egyptian is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 9. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the photographer is on the left or right of the analyst##3
11. the photographer is the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | photography    | magic-tricks  | filmmaking | hiking   |
| Job           | project-manager | photographer   | analyst    | nurse |
| Nationality   | nigerian      | egyptian | turkish | indonesian  |

