2. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person eating banana##1
3. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far right##1
5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person eating potato##3
8. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
