4. the software-developer is on the right of the mechanic##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
7. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
