4. the dancer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
7. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
