.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, tea, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, security-guard, fisherman, chef
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, tram, scooter, bus
1. the chef is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the security-guard##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
6. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the tram and the person drinking milk##2
7. the person drinking fanta is the security-guard##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | fanta   | tea   | milk    | water |
| Job         | security-guard | fisherman    | designer      | chef |
| Transport   | tram      | bus | scooter | van   |

