.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, mirinda, sprite
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, skydiving, camping, gardening
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, tram, helicopter, bike
1. the person drinking lemonade is the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the bike##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
8. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
9. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is gardening##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate      | lemonade | sprite       | mirinda  |
| Hobby       | camping | singing | gardening    | skydiving |
| Transport   | tram     | boat         | helicopter | bike     |

