4. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the trike##2
5. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
8. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

