.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, time-travel, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, subway, jet-ski
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person watching superhero movies and the person driving the subway##2
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate      | soy-milk     | tea | lemonade |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | satire    | superhero   | mystery |
| Transport     | subway | scooter | jet-ski   | quad-bike    |

