.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, coffee, milk
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, lemon, spinach
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, american, turkish, colombian
1. the colombian is on the left of the australian##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
5. the american is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
6. the person eating spinach is on the left of the australian##1
7. the person drinking fanta is the turkish##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking soy-milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | fanta | milk    | soy-milk | coffee  |
| Food          | cabbage          | artichoke | spinach       | lemon      |
| Nationality   | turkish     | american    | colombian     | australian |

