.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, lettuce, cucumber, eggplant
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, coach, paramedic, manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, snowboarding, badminton
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the police-officer##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person eating tomato and the person eating cucumber##2
6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the manager##3
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the paramedic##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | cucumber | lettuce  | tomato  | eggplant           |
| Job     | police-officer | paramedic | coach   | manager |
| Sport   | badminton   | lacrosse       | climbing | snowboarding  |

 